snippet.title: Stargate Network v4.0 - Virtual Stargate Exploration Tour
snippet.description:
Stargate Network is an Fan project, that provides an interactive Fan experience. Fans can do a virtual Stargate Exploration tour. 
In the current version is the Stargate Center included as well as Abydoss and two further planets.

The Homepage of this project is: www.stargate-network.net

 Enjoy
